        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.1</title>
            <sparkle:version>2603211532</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.1.1</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Close to menu bar</b> — Closing the window no longer quits the app. Remio Host stays running in the background with a menu bar icon.</li>
                    <li><b>Menu bar status indicator</b> — A colored dot shows your streaming status at a glance: 🟢 streaming, 🟠 connecting, 🔴 error, ⚫ idle.</li>
                    <li><b>Quick actions from menu bar</b> — Start/stop streaming, show the main window, or quit from the menu bar dropdown.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
