            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.1.0</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>File Transfer</b> — Send files from your phone directly to your Mac</li>
                    <li><b>Improved Presence System</b> — More accurate online/streaming status</li>
                    <li>Optimized streaming engine for better responsiveness</li>
                    <li>Improved connection stability and reconnection logic</li>
                    <li>Fixed OOBE permission flow for seamless first-time setup</li>
                    <li>Bug fixes and performance improvements</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
